    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs required level 3) is mitigated by the explicit COU scope restriction to standard ASTM F1717 conditions and by the strong output comparison results (all E/uval < 0.9). The FEA ensemble is judged credible for the stated COU. Submission to FDA supported.",
